sections.heading: practitioner; right to use title or abbreviation
sections.text: A person licensed to practice as a nurse practitioner in this state may use the title nurse practitioner and the abbreviation NP.SourceLaws 1984, LB 724, § 27;Laws 1996, LB 414, § 32;Laws 2000, LB 1115, § 48;Laws 2005, LB 256, § 61;R.S.Supp.,2006, § 7
